    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2>This Blog</h2>

<p>This is the only link you really need for the project. I&rsquo;ll add any updates, designs, notes, etc. here and then email you the link.</p>

<h2><a href="https://trello.com/b/wRGms9of">Trello</a></h2>

<p>We will use <a href="https://trello.com/b/wRGms9of">this board to keep track of all the bits for the project</a>: tasks with associated copy, images, comments, etc..</p>

<p>I&rsquo;ve made a <strong>To Do</strong> column for Big and I. Big stands for anyone that is working with David.</p>

<p>You simply drag-n-drop the cards from column to column.</p>

<p><img src="http://big.solutiondrop.com/images/Fullscreen_6_18_14__10_00_AM.png" alt="" /></p>

<p>Each card can have comments, checklists for sub-tasks, due date and attachments (e.g., images).</p>

<p><img src="http://big.solutiondrop.com/images/Fullscreen_6_18_14__10_13_AM.png" alt="" /></p>

<p>There is a calendar for cards with due dates:</p>

<p><img src="http://big.solutiondrop.com/images/Fullscreen_6_18_14__10_19_AM.png" alt="" /></p>
